      "rationale": "Primary QoI is construct stiffness (N/mm) and peak rod surface strain (με). NRMSE across 11 constructs: stiffness 4.8%, strain 6.3%. Both within acceptance threshold. Bland-Altman analysis confirms no systematic bias."
