      "rationale": "Construct stiffness and rod surface strain are the primary outputs specified in ASTM F1717 and referenced in FDA guidance for pedicle screw 510(k) submissions. Clinical relevance confirmed by spine biomechanics subject matter expert panel."
    },
    {
