    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted at Medium assurance level. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) is accepted given the validation scope is explicitly bounded to the ASTM F1717 static compression-bending regulatory submission context for non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screws, as described in the Claim and Requirement documentation. Risk of extrapolation beyond this loading condition is acknowledged and communicated to the regulatory decision-maker.",
